$project8 = Project::create(['name' => ' Stadium seating','open_date' => '2018-06-30 0:00:00','close_date' => '2018-07-02 0:00:00','prompt' => '\n<div>There are three seating categories at an athletic stadium. Class A seats cost $15 each, Class B seats cost $12 each, and Class C seats cost $9 each. Create an application that allows the user to enter the number of tickets sold for each class. The application should be able to display the amount of income generated from each class of ticket sales and the total revenue generated. The output should look something like the following: \n<table class="code-padded">\n<col align="right">\n<col align="left">\n<col align="left">\n<tr><td/><td># Tickets</td><td>Revenue</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Class A:</td><td>320</td><td>$4,800</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Class B:</td><td>570</td><td>$6,840</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Class C:</td><td>890</td><td>$8,010</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Total:</td><td>1780</td><td>$19,650</td></tr>\n</table>\nThe output must be formatted using the string format() function.\n<p>If ticket sales exceeds $20,000 print "Meets projections." Otherwise, print "Did not meet projections." This will let the user know whether they need to ramp up advertising for the next event or not.\n<p>Your code should have the following variables: <span class="code">costA, costB, costC, numA, numB, numC, numTotal, revenueA, revenueB, revenueC, revenueTotal</span>.\n</div>\n','pre_code' => '','start_code' => '','solution' => 'classA = 15\nclassB = 12\nclassC = 9\nnumA = int(input("Number of class A tickets:"))\nnumB = int(input("Number of class B tickets:"))\nnumC = int(input("Number of class C tickets:"))\nnumTotal = numA + numB + numC\nrevenueA = classA*numA\nrevenueB = classB*numB\nrevenueC = classC*numC\nrevenueTotal = revenueA + revenueB + revenueC\nprint("{:>8}  {:<10}{:<10}".format("", "# Tickets", "Revenue"))\nprint("{:>8}  {:<10}${:,}".format("Class A:", numA, revenueA))\nprint("{:>8}  {:<10}${:,}".format("Class B:", numB, revenueB))\nprint("{:>8}  {:<10}${:,}".format("Class C:", numC, revenueC))\nprint("{:>8}  {:<10}${:,}".format("Total:", numTotal, revenueTotal))\nif revenueTotal > 20000:\n    print("Meets projections.")\nelse\n    print("Did not meet projections.")\n','module_id' => $module8->id,'previous_lesson_id' => $lesson15->id,'user_id' => $user->id]);
